{
  "stem": "21582.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So it was-- there really was a, a psychological preparation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were slogans.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We are fortified and strong.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And nobody will ever overrun Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And if the Germans will come, there's no way that they'll come in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we are better.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we are superior.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they are not going-- so this preparation, the build-up, was very-- a drumming up of patriotism.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was a great deal of, of, of that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, but you see, the Jewish-- the patriot-- whether the Jews were wrapped up in the patriotism, in a sense, in a sense, yes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, but I don't know what this word connotes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I want to, to, to explain.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Jewish people were Polish people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for us, this was our home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was-- this was-- this was our safety.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that we were set apart, it's almost like being orphaned.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, when people say-- after I, I share my stories about how I was treated as a child and they say, do you still feel Polish?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I say, yes and no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- no, I am definitely Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And definitely I am not Polish because they didn't let me be Polish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then I was Polish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I, I felt-- I, I felt an equal claim.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- I feel that I was kicked out of my home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this was my home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was my beautiful city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is-- this is where I-- where, where-- this was my sky.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "These were my trees.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This, this, this was everything that, that fed my soul.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So yes, in that sense, that was mine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, and of course, when the country was threatened, all of us were threatened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In that sense, sure, the Jewish people were mobilized, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because there was a mobilization.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
